overview: Niko Kivelä and Sami Hedberg, the steamingers of the corner grills, land like the Fenix ​​bird at the Sibelius House in Lahti and, like the Felix ketchup, download the sparrow flock of high-flying lips now also directly to your home sofa. The feathers dust, the chicks hatch and the feathers melt smoothly as this duo begins their chicken flight. Never have your lips flown so high! There has never been so much turbulence on stage! And there have never been so many spectators in a club of ten. So put your wings on your back and jump in!  Now let's go! Also present will host the evening stand Up comedian Zaani.
title: Wings of Comedy
